t-verification.md:17:   `./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=<g:a:v> --agentAllowedPackages=fromJar\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:30:   `./gradlew runNativeTraceImage`; the trace binary is built with\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:66:| Per-cycle timeout | `cycle_timeout_seconds` argument | Default 30 minutes. Caps the preflight `./gradlew test` invocation and each `runNativeTraceImage` invocation; on timeout the step is treated as a non-zero exit and routed to codex. |\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:74:  staged JVM-agent metadata when `generateMetadata` succeeds.\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:82:  Gradle log (`generateMetadata`, `test`, or `runNativeTraceImage`).\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:99:    Init --> Agent[gradlew generateMetadata<br/>--agentAllowedPackages=fromJar<br/>--metadataOutputDir=agent_dir]\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:107:    Outer -- yes --> Run[gradlew runNativeTraceImage<br/>-PtraceMetadataPath=runs/cycle-i<br/>-PtraceMetadataConditionPackages=&lt;packages&gt;<br/>-PmetadataConfigDirs=&lt;config_dirs&gt;]\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:109:    Route -- 0 --> MergeTrace[mergeNativeTraceMetadata<br/>accepted trace dirs &rarr; trace_dir]\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:125:  `./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=<g:a:v>\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:141:  `./gradlew runNativeTraceImage -Pcoordinates=<g:a:v>\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:142:  -PtraceMetadataPath=<runs_dir>/cycle-<i>\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:155:    test are sufficient. The gate runs `mergeNativeTraceMetadata` to\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:168:    **not** re-run `runNativeTraceImage` after codex.\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:231:- `./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=...\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:238:- `./gradlew runNativeTraceImage -Pcoordinates=...\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:239:  -PtraceMetadataPath=<runs_dir>/cycle-<i>\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:242:- `./gradlew mergeNativeTraceMetadata -PinputDirs=...\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:245:- `./gradlew mergeNativeTraceMetadata -PinputDirs=...\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:280:   `./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=...\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:289:5. Each fallback outer cycle invokes `./gradlew runNativeTraceImage\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:290:   -Pcoordinates=... -PtraceMetadataPath=<runs_dir>/cycle-<i>\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:296:   - `0` → run `mergeNativeTraceMetadata` once with all accepted run\\n./forge/docs/native-test-verification.md:312:     `runNativeTraceImage` after codex.\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:24:        Finalize[\\\"_finalize_successful_iteration<br/>(generateMetadata + commit)\\\"]\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:52:        Repo[(\\\"Reachability repo<br/>./gradlew test, generateMetadata,<br/>checkMetadataFiles, splitTestOnlyMetadata\\\")]\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:81:    Trace -.->|gradlew nativeTraceImage,<br/>runNativeTraceImage,<br/>mergeNativeTraceMetadata| Repo\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:121:  `generateMetadata` (with `--agentAllowedPackages=fromJar`),\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:313:   `nativeTraceImage` → `runNativeTraceImage` → optional\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:314:   `mergeNativeTraceMetadata` until convergence, build failure, or the\\n./forge/docs/dynamic-access-workflow.md:42:  / `generateMetadata` step (in benchmark mode, only `generateMetadata` runs).\\n./forge/docs/dynamic-access-workflow.md:93:    Wrap --> Final[Finalization<br/>generateMetadata &rarr; exploration &rarr; codex &rarr; commit]\\n./forge/docs/dynamic-access-workflow.md:218:./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=<g:a:v> --agentAllowedPackages=fromJar --metadataOutputDir=<output_dir>/agent\\n./forge/docs/dynamic-acce