l next steps:\n1. Replace the scaffold test with real library-specific tests for `groovy.test.GroovyAssert` / `groovy.test.AllTestSuite`, and verify whether extra test/runtime deps such as `groovy-ant` are required.\n2. Reproduce `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.groovy:groovy-test:4.0.24` under the intended GraalVM and debug the `GroovySystem` initialization failure in native mode.\n3. After native tests are stable, rerun metadata generation in an environment where the `native-image-agent` library is available."}}
